gnome-perl: gnome-perl (GNOME Bindings for Perl)
gnome-perl:
gnome-perl: gnome-perl is a set of perl bindings for Gtk+2 and GNOME libraries. 
gnome-perl: These modules make it easy to write GTK and GNOME applications using 
gnome-perl: Perl. It includes the Glib, Gtk2, Gnome2-VFS, Gnome2-GConf, 
gnome-perl: Gnome2-Canvas, and Gnome2 bindings for perl.
